        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>如果你想在本站发布你的文章，请阅读下面的发布流程。</p>
<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_YgRK" id="1-部署本地环境">1. 部署本地环境<a href="https://arcadia.cool/blog/welcome#1-%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83" class="hash-link" aria-label="1. 部署本地环境的直接链接" title="1. 部署本地环境的直接链接">​</a></h2>
<p>首先，请克隆本仓库到本地并进入根目录</p>
<div class="language-bash codeBlockContainer_ybqk theme-code-block" style="--prism-background-color:hsl(230, 1%, 98%);--prism-color:hsl(230, 8%, 24%)"><div class="codeBlockContent_WD_w"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-bash codeBlock_Ziq1 thin-scrollbar" style="background-color:hsl(230, 1%, 98%);color:hsl(230, 8%, 24%)"><code class="codeBlockLines_Giy0"><span class="token-line" style="color:hsl(230, 8%, 24%)"><span class="token function" style="color:hsl(221, 87%, 60%)">git</span><span class="token plain"> clone </span><span class="token parameter variable" style="color:hsl(221, 87%, 60%)">-b</span><span class="token plain"> website https://github.com/SuperManito/Arcadia.git</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:hsl(230, 8%, 24%)"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token builtin class-name" style="color:hsl(35, 99%, 36%)">cd</span><span class="token plain"> Arcadia</span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup_QBAz"><button type="button" aria-label="复制代码到剪贴板" title="复制" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_rAUe" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonIcon_FrPv"><path fill="currentColor" d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_CNTZ"><path fill="currentColor" d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div>
<p>接着，你需要安装依赖并运行本地开发服务器（预览）</p>
<div class="tabs-container tabList_r0Pk"><ul role="tablist" aria-orientation="horizontal" class="tabs"><li role="tab" tabindex="0" aria-selected="true" class="tabs__item tabItem_JG85 tabs__item--active">npm</li><li role="tab" tabindex="-1" aria-selected="false" class="tabs__item tabItem_JG85">Yarn</li><li role="tab" tabindex="-1" aria-selected="false" class="tabs__item tabItem_JG85">pnpm</li></ul><div class="margin-top--md"><div role="tabpanel" class="tabItem_nQZO"><div class="language-bash codeBlockContainer_ybqk theme-code-block" style="--prism-background-color:hsl(230, 1%, 98%);--prism-color:hsl(230, 8%, 24%)"><div class="codeBlockContent_WD_w"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-bash codeBlock_Ziq1 thin-scrollbar" style="background-color:hsl(230, 1%, 98%);color:hsl(230, 8%, 24%)"><code class="codeBlockLines_Giy0"><span class="token-line" style="color:hsl(230, 8%, 24%)"><span class="token function" style="color:hsl(221, 87%, 60%)">npm</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token function" style="color:hsl(221, 87%, 60%)">install</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:hsl(230, 8%, 24%)"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token function" style="color:hsl(221, 87%, 60%)">npm</span><span class="token plain"> run start</span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup_QBAz"><button type="button" aria-label="复制代码到剪贴板" title="复制" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_rAUe" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonIcon_FrPv"><path fill="currentColor" d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_CNTZ"><path fill="currentColor" d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div></div><div role="tabpanel" class="tabItem_nQZO" hidden=""><div class="language-bash codeBlockContainer_ybqk theme-code-block" style="--prism-background-color:hsl(230, 1%, 98%);--prism-color:hsl(230, 8%, 24%)"><div class="codeBlockContent_WD_w"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-bash codeBlock_Ziq1 thin-scrollbar" style="background-color:hsl(230, 1%, 98%);color:hsl(230, 8%, 24%)"><code class="codeBlockLines_Giy0"><span class="token-line" style="color:hsl(230, 8%, 24%)"><span class="token function" style="color:hsl(221, 87%, 60%)">yarn</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token function" style="color:hsl(221, 87%, 60%)">install</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:hsl(230, 8%, 24%)"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token function" style="color:hsl(221, 87%, 60%)">yarn</span><span class="token plain"> run start</span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup_QBAz"><button type="button" aria-label="复制代码到剪贴板" title="复制" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_rAUe" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonIcon_FrPv"><path fill="currentColor" d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_CNTZ"><path fill="currentColor" d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div></div><div role="tabpanel" class="tabItem_nQZO" hidden=""><div class="language-bash codeBlockContainer_ybqk theme-code-block" style="--prism-background-color:hsl(230, 1%, 98%);--prism-color:hsl(230, 8%, 24%)"><div class="codeBlockContent_WD_w"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-bash codeBlock_Ziq1 thin-scrollbar" style="background-color:hsl(230, 1%, 98%);color:hsl(230, 8%, 24%)"><code class="codeBlockLines_Giy0"><span class="token-line" style="color:hsl(230, 8%, 24%)"><span class="token function" style="color:hsl(221, 87%, 60%)">pnpm</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token function" style="color:hsl(221, 87%, 60%)">install</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:hsl(230, 8%, 24%)"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token function" style="color:hsl(221, 87%, 60%)">pnpm</span><span class="token plain"> run start</span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup_QBAz"><button type="button" aria-label="复制代码到剪贴板" title="复制" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_rAUe" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonIcon_FrPv"><path fill="currentColor" d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_CNTZ"><path fill="currentColor" d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div></div></div></div>
<p>默认情况下，系统浏览器会自动打开一个窗口 <a href="http://localhost:3000/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">http://localhost:3000</a></p>
<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_YgRK" id="2-创建博客">2. 创建博客<a href="https://arcadia.cool/blog/welcome#2-%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2" class="hash-link" aria-label="2. 创建博客的直接链接" title="2. 创建博客的直接链接">​</a></h2>
<p>在 <code>blog</code> 目录下创建一个 <code>.md</code> 或 <code>.mdx</code> 文件，文件名需要使用英文，格式为 <code>yyyy-mm-dd-文章标题.md</code>，例如：<code>2024-05-01-welcome.md</code>，之后你就可以在本地开发服务器的博客页面看到这篇文章了。</p>
<p>如果你需要在内容中添加图片等媒体资源，那么你需要在 blog 目录下按照命名规则建立一个文件夹例如 <code>2024-05-01-welcome</code>，然后将文件命名为 <code>index.md</code> 或 <code>index.mdx</code>，这样你就可以在博客中使用相对路径引用这些资源了。</p>
<div class="language-bash codeBlockContainer_ybqk theme-code-block" style="--prism-background-color:hsl(230, 1%, 98%);--prism-color:hsl(230, 8%, 24%)"><div class="codeBlockContent_WD_w"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-bash codeBlock_Ziq1 thin-scrollbar" style="background-color:hsl(230, 1%, 98%);color:hsl(230, 8%, 24%)"><code class="codeBlockLines_Giy0"><span class="token-line" style="color:hsl(230, 8%, 24%)"><span class="token plain">blog</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:hsl(230, 8%, 24%)"><span class="token plain">  └── </span><span class="token number" style="color:hsl(35, 99%, 36%)">2024</span><span class="token plain">-05-01-welcome</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:hsl(230, 8%, 24%)"><span class="token plain">      ├── index.md</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:hsl(230, 8%, 24%)"><span class="token plain">      └── image.png</span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup_QBAz"><button type="button" aria-label="复制代码到剪贴板" title="复制" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_rAUe" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonIcon_FrPv"><path fill="currentColor" d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_CNTZ"><path fill="currentColor" d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div>
<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_YgRK" id="3-编辑博客">3. 编辑博客<a href="https://arcadia.cool/blog/welcome#3-%E7%BC%96%E8%BE%91%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2" class="hash-link" aria-label="3. 编辑博客的直接链接" title="3. 编辑博客的直接链接">​</a></h2>
<ul>
<li>
<h3 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_YgRK" id="博客前言">博客前言<a href="https://arcadia.cool/blog/welcome#%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E5%89%8D%E8%A8%80" class="hash-link" aria-label="博客前言的直接链接" title="博客前言的直接链接">​</a></h3>
<p>这是一个示例，有关更多配置字段详见 <a href="https://docusaurus.io/zh-CN/docs/api/plugins/@docusaurus/plugin-content-blog#markdown-front-matter" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Markdown 前言</a></p>
<div class="language-bash codeBlockContainer_ybqk theme-code-block" style="--prism-background-color:hsl(230, 1%, 98%);--prism-color:hsl(230, 8%, 24%)"><div class="codeBlockContent_WD_w"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-bash codeBlock_Ziq1 thin-scrollbar" style="background-color:hsl(230, 1%, 98%);color:hsl(230, 8%, 24%)"><code class="codeBlockLines_Giy0"><span class="token-line" style="color:hsl(230, 8%, 24%)"><span class="token plain">---</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:hsl(230, 8%, 24%)"><span class="token plain">slug: </span><span class="token builtin class-name" style="color:hsl(35, 99%, 36%)">test</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token comment" style="color:hsl(230, 4%, 64%)"># 路径(url)，你可以自定义这一路径，尽量保持精简且唯一</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:hsl(230, 8%, 24%)"><span class="token plain">title: 欢迎来到博客 </span><span class="token comment" style="color:hsl(230, 4%, 64%)"># 标题</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:hsl(230, 8%, 24%)"><span class="token plain">authors: user </span><span class="token comment" style="color:hsl(230, 4%, 64%)"># 作者，需要在 authors.yml 进行配置</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:hsl(230, 8%, 24%)"><span class="token plain">tags: </span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:hsl(119, 34%, 47%)">[</span><span class="token string" style="color:hsl(119, 34%, 47%)">'教程'</span><span class="token plain">, </span><span class="token string" style="color:hsl(119, 34%, 47%)">'新手'</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:hsl(119, 34%, 47%)">]</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token comment" style="color:hsl(230, 4%, 64%)"># 底部标签</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:hsl(230, 8%, 24%)"><span class="token plain">---</span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup_QBAz"><button type="button" aria-label="复制代码到剪贴板" title="复制" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_rAUe" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonIcon_FrPv"><path fill="currentColor" d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_CNTZ"><path fill="currentColor" d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div>
</li>
<li>
<h3 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_YgRK" id="博客内容">博客内容<a href="https://arcadia.cool/blog/welcome#%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9" class="hash-link" aria-label="博客内容的直接链接" title="博客内容的直接链接">​</a></h3>
<p>如果你不熟悉 Markdown 语法那么请先学习 <a href="https://docs.github.com/zh/get-started/writing-on-github/getting-started-with-writing-and-formatting-on-github/basic-writing-and-formatting-syntax" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Markdown 基本撰写和格式语法</a>，这是一个简单的语法，你可以很快学会。</p>
<p>本站基于 <a href="https://docusaurus.io/zh-CN" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Docusaurus</a> 构建，你可以通过官网教程学习使用 <a href="https://docusaurus.io/zh-CN/docs/markdown-features" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Markdown 特性</a></p>
</li>
</ul>
